R5 is phenyl, pyridyl, or isothiazolyl, wherein each phenyl, pyridyl, or isothiazolyl moiety is optionally substituted by 1 or 2 substituents, which may be the same or different, selected from R7;
R6 is methyl; and
R7 is methyl.

